properties.headline: Wind Advisory issued February 17 at 2:19PM EST until February 18 at 10:00PM EST by NWS Burlington VT
properties.description:
* WHAT...South winds 25 to 35 mph with gusts up to 50 mph
expected.

* WHERE...In Vermont, Grand Isle County. In New York, Franklin and
Clinton counties.

* WHEN...From 7 AM to 10 PM EST Tuesday.

* IMPACTS...Gusty winds could blow around unsecured objects.
Tree limbs could be blown down and a few power outages may
result.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...The core of the strongest winds will occur
between 10 AM and 7 PM on Tuesday.
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.

NWSheadline: WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 7 AM TO 10 PM EST TUESDAY
